{"word":"G2564 - καλέω - kaléō - kal-eh'-o - Bid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kaléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kal-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பேரிடு, அழை, சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. to call"},{"paragraph":"2. to name, call by name"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G2753 - κελεύω - keleúō - kel-yoo'-o/2753\">G2753</a>; to &ldquo;call&rdquo; (properly aloud, but used in a variety of applications, directly or otherwise): - bid, call (forth), (whose, whose sur-) name (was [called]).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1458/1458\">G1458</a>, <a href=\"#/G1462/1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528/1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1577/1577\">G1577</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941/1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2564/2564\">G2564</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821/2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822/2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G3333/3333\">G3333</a>, <a href=\"#/G4292/4292\">G4292</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341/4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779/4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479/479\">G479</a>"}]}